#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.hypot.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.hypot"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:1 of
msgid "Given the \"legs\" of a right triangle, return its hypotenuse."
msgstr "给定直角三角形的“直角边”，返回其斜边。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:3 of
msgid ""
"Equivalent to ``sqrt(x1**2 + x2**2)``, element-wise.  If `x1` or `x2` is "
"scalar_like (i.e., unambiguously cast-able to a scalar type), it is "
"broadcast for use with each element of the other argument. (See Examples)"
msgstr ""
"等价于 ``sqrt(x1**2 + x2**2)``，逐元素计算。如果 `x1` 或 `x2` 是标量类型"
"（即可以明确地转换为标量类型），它将被广播以与另一个参数的每个元素一起"
"使用。（参见示例）"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:8
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:10 of
msgid "Leg of the triangle(s)."
msgstr "三角形的直角边。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:12 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated array is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播后的形状一致。如果未"
"提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的数组。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度"
"必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:17 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:22 of
msgid "**z** -- The hypotenuse of the triangle(s)."
msgstr "**z** -- 三角形的斜边。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:26 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.hypot.hypot:34 of
msgid "Example showing broadcast of scalar_like argument:"
msgstr "展示标量类型参数广播的示例："

